{"tid":2270104,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【mma】 事實證明，最愛波台假膠post既就係時事台會員!","createTime":"2020-11-04T01:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T03:13:07.000Z","uid":34571,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"62908465e28c5dfa87475c0fd242aaa4a1d7a0fc","tid":2270104,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:12:32.000Z","msg":"已經ig pm 咗牙朗， 希望佢會同香港人打氣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1231881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1231881</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一年幾前開咗依個post, 想發起大家pm球星， 結果無人理得波台手足支持。但調轉一有人開膠post cctai軍團就沖入去留言。 其實cctai 班人心態就係波台友邊有資格做認真野，只有佢地先有資格做依啲改變世界既事。<br />\n<br />\n波台友做實事＝冷處理<br />\n波台友開膠post= 沖入去留言<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，邊班人最中意分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb4f3b2bcc29507a380ee2ce051e7f5eca52e8e","tid":2270104,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:15:04.000Z","msg":"波台狗開膠post佢地先有嘢做嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290f09a4fc544981ef91855a2b1cecf5f5e16a34","tid":2270104,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fb4f3b2bcc29507a380ee2ce051e7f5eca52e8e","tid":2270104,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:15:04.000Z","msg":"波台狗開膠post佢地先有嘢做嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:16:24.000Z","msg":"joker, batman， 無波台友開post佢地人生少咗好多樂趣"},{"pid":"5127f0430e7430a5702167a0b9efbb093458603e","tid":2270104,"uid":248695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"佢哋要狙擊波台清當光復咗香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c23e36b55dc2c7362d0e8990737283b158e963","tid":2270104,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T02:20:54.000Z","msg":"叫人守理大、水人送中既po就扮睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n波台假膠就咬到實一實"},{"pid":"99151a64c2d2ad15f42ad9976